{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 74,
  "title": "第七十四章（司殺）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "若民恆且不畏死，奈何以殺懼之也？"
    },
    {
      "text": "若民恆是畏死，則而為者，吾得而殺之，夫孰敢矣？"
    },
    {
      "text": "若民恆且必畏死，則恆有司殺者。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫代司殺者殺，是代大匠斵也。夫代大匠斵者，則希不傷亓手矣。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 16,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "治國者刑罰酷深，民不聊生，故不畏死也。治身者嗜欲傷神，貪財殺身，民不知畏之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 16,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人君不寬刑罰，教民去情欲，奈何設刑法以死懼之？若使民常畏死，當除己之所殘剋，教民去利欲也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 23,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以道教化而民不從，反為奇巧，乃應王法執而殺之，誰敢有犯者？老子傷時王不先道德化之，而先刑罰也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "司殺者謂天，居高臨下，司察人過。天網恢恢，疏而不失也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 15,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天道至明，司殺有常，猶春生夏長，秋收冬藏，斗杓運移，以節度行之。人君欲代殺之，是猶拙夫代大匠斲木，勞而無功也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 29,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人君行刑罰，猶拙夫代大匠斲，則方圓不得其理，還自傷。代天殺者，失紀綱，不得其紀綱還受其殃也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 23,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "詭異亂群謂之奇也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 15,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "為逆順者之所惡忿也，不仁者人之所疾也。故曰，常有司殺也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
